    "en": {
      "title": "Lanka Premier League 2022 postponed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka Cricket (SLC) has announced that the Lanka Premier League 2022 has been postponed.",
        "Accordingly, the Lanka Premir League, which was scheduled to be held from 1st to 21st August, 2022 will be postponed, with immediate effect.",
        "This decision was taken by the SLC, following a request made by the Innovative Production Group FZE (IPG), the Rights Holder of the tournament, which cited the current \u2018economic situation,\u2019 in the country, as not conducive to hosting the tournament.",
        "Indian Govt calls for all-party meeting over Sri Lankan crisis",
        "Japan engages in high level talks with CBSL & Treasury officials"
      ],
